OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FRape cases should be tried 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fin specialist courts, says 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Freport                     
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Specialist courts dealing solely with  
OL,6, rape offences are needed to reduce a   
OL,7, large case backlog and reduce victims' 
OL,8, trauma, a watchdogs' report urges.     
OL,10,FThe BBC understands that Deputy Prime  
OL,11,FMinister Dominic Raab is taking advice 
OL,12,Fon the feasibility of such courts.     
OL,14,FVictims of rape are being failed by a  
OL,15,Fsystem beset by delays and poor        
OL,16,Fcommunication, the report by the police
OL,17,Fand prosecution service watchdogs says.
OL,19,FOne victim told the authors her court  
OL,20,Fexperience had been "horrendous".      
